channel.title: [Proposed] for org-id, a new list JO-MSD: Register of Associations (Jordan)
channel.description:
A new list has been proposed with the code JO-MSD after a request from an IATI publisher.
**List title:** Register of Associations - Ministry of Social Development, Jordan
The Ministry registers NGOs which can be searched at http://www.societies.gov.jo/
Check the files changed options https://github.com/org-id/register/pull/173/files. (the org-id.guide preview platform is currently disabled).
Unless objections are raised, this update will be merged after 7 days.
